Name: Adventures of Quin85
About the game: Welcome to the world of Clowns You are a clown! (ingame) (meme) Become a famous streamer and destroy games without breaking a sweat. On your Adventure you will find allies that will lend you their strength. Fight powerful Bosses and Enemies Powerful base skills create an almost infinite Skill ceiling. This game will show you how good you actually are at Games. Your reaction speed and adaptability will be key to your success. Dash and bash through enemies to reset your jump and bash on. Once you make it through a zone a powerful Boss is awaiting you. Starting easy they will gradually become harder and harder with every zone you leave behind you. In Chapter 1 you will: - Play through the beginnings of a scuffed Story - Beat 5 very hard Zones with dangerous obstacles - Fight 5 powerful Bosses - Learn 4 unique abilities The rest of the game is still in active development
